# Beantol Messenger Bot — Feature Roadmap

When the user asks what still needs doing, what's left on the checklist, or roadmap status, refer here. Legend: **DONE** | **PARTIAL** | **NOT STARTED**.

## Core AI & knowledge
| Feature | Status | Where / notes |
|---------|--------|---------------|
| AI chatbot (OpenAI LLM) | DONE | `system-rules.js` + RAG knowledge + `openai.chat.completions` |
| AI trained on business documents (RAG/PDF upload) | DONE | Google Docs sync, `lib/rag.js`, `knowledge/templates/` backup |
| Conversation memory | DONE | `CHAT_HISTORY_*` env, chat history maps |
| Multi-language (EN/TL/Cebuano) | DONE | `detectReplyLanguagePreference`, `getReplyLanguageInstruction` |

